{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_6389d174-6740-4bd5-a6ff-5171d4b02c2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md","limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 第一幕《打错电话》· 画布 mock 拓扑（代码事实）\n\n> 正式稿（仓外）：`doubaoSister/.../定稿的故事/1.第一幕初识.md`（标题《打错电话》）。  \n> 代码：`CanvasMockGraph.ts` + `CanvasMockGraph.edges.ts`。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22。用户评语：「稍微有点偏差，但是很准确了」。\n\n## 1. 包 / 章节展示名\n\n| 键 | 当前值 | 说明 |\n|----|--------|------|\n| `packageId` | `pkg_memory_bar_1` | **历史 id 未改**（路由/种子兼容）；勿从 id 推断剧情仍是「内存条」 |\n| 列表 title | `第一幕：打错电话` | `mockWorkbenchData.ts` |\n| 顶栏 chapterTitle | `第一幕 · 打错电话` | `StoryEditorShell` |\n| chapter_start.title | 同上 | 画布节点 |\n| entryCardId | `lanxing_wrong_number` | `packageConfProjection` DEFAULT 种子 |\n\n## 2. 卡拓扑（业务理解）\n\n```text\nchapter_start\n    → card_wrong_number「打错电话」(lanxing, outbound_auto)\n         exit_callback「挂机后补打」\n           effects: attach_call_card → lanxing_callback_intro\n                    schedule_call_card delayMinutes=2\n           story 边 + attach 效果边 → card_callback\n    → card_callback「补打自报」\n         exit_known「记住名号」→ end_story → chapter_end\n         exit_voicemail「没说清→留言」→ create_voicemail → card_voicemail\n    → card_voicemail「语音留言」→ end_story → chapter_end\nchapter_end.summary：小皮收拾书包 / 纸条 / 拿起电话（下章钩子，无独立小皮卡）\n```\n\n三张卡 **均归属澜星**；左侧五人锚点仍在，强叔叔等仅台词提及。\n\n## 3. 与正式稿节拍对照\n\n| 正式稿节拍 | mock 落点 | 偏差备注 |\n|------------|-----------|----------|\n| 第一次误拨、闲聊、不留名号挂断 | `card_wrong_number` | speakable 为压缩台词，非逐句剧本 |\n| 补打自报、问称呼、留 2267070、提小皮露营 | `card_callback` | 「告诉名字 / 不告诉」收敛成两条出口，非复杂条件 DSL |","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":58,"fileSize":2885,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":40},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_6389d174-6740-4bd5-a6ff-5171d4b02c2","startedAtMs":"1